@page "/chinh-sach-van-chuyen"
@model ShippingPolicyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Chinh sach van chuyen";
    ViewData["Description"] = "Thong tin giao hang, phi van chuyen va thoi gian xu ly don hang CoPuree.";
}

<section class="policy-page">
    <p class="eyebrow">Giao hang</p>
    <h1>Chinh sach van chuyen</h1>
    <p>CoPuree xac nhan don trong vong 24 gio lam viec sau khi khach hang dat hang tren website. Kho gui hang hien tai: Vinhomes Grand Park, Long Binh, Thu Duc.</p>
    <h2>Phi van chuyen</h2>
    <p>Phi mac dinh hien tai la 30.000 d. Don hang tu 500.000 d duoc mien phi van chuyen trong giai doan ra mat.</p>
    <h2>Thoi gian giao hang</h2>
    <p>Noi thanh thuong tu 1-3 ngay lam viec. Cac tinh thanh khac thuong tu 3-5 ngay lam viec tuy don vi van chuyen.</p>
    <h2>Kiem tra hang</h2>
    <p>Khach hang nen kiem tra tinh trang dong goi khi nhan hang va lien he CoPuree neu san pham bi vo, ro ri hoac sai so luong.</p>
</section>
